    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Sonerila reptans J. Wai & J.-M. Hu.A. Habit, B. Bract, C. Flower, D. Petals showing adaxial surface (left), abaxial surfaces (central) and side view (right), E. Stamen, F. Longitudinal section of a flower showing hypanthium, stigma, style and ovary. G. Immature fruits. H. Fruit.All from J. Wai 2641 (PSU). Drawn by P. Tippayasri." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10011177/files/figure.png" ;
