    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Photos of Sonerila reptans J. Wai & J.-M. Hu. A. Habit and habitat, B. Habit showing flowering shoots with leaves, C. Inflorescences, D. Fruits, E. Seed, lateral view, F. Seed showing verrucose papillae and tubercles on antiraphal side. Photos by J. Sae Wai." ;
